      "reason_en": "Spain are 2026 World Cup champions, beating Argentina 1-0 in extra time in the final (July 19, East Rutherford, NJ). Ferran Torres struck 39 seconds into the second period of extra time, with Argentina reduced to 10 men after Enzo Fernández's second yellow card in second-half stoppage time. It's Spain's second world title, their first since 2010; Messi was held scoreless in his self-declared final World Cup match.",
      "reason_zh": "西班牙夺得2026年世界杯冠军，决赛加时1-0淘汰阿根廷（7 月 19 日，新泽西东卢瑟福）。加时赛下半场开始仅39秒，费兰·托雷斯打入制胜球；此前恩佐·费尔南德斯在下半场补时阶段第二黄变一红被罚下，阿根廷少打一人。这是西班牙队史第二座世界杯冠军，也是2010年以来的首次夺冠；梅西在他自称的谢幕之战中颗粒无收。"
    }
